window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>An action packed LitRPG adventure perfect for fans of Solo Leveling, The Primal Hunter, and 1% Lifesteal!</i></p> <p><b>Alone. Surrounded by monsters. Time to fight his way up the food chain.</b></p> <p>In the aftermath of an unprecedented magical disaster, Edge wakes up in a monster-infested wilderness, standing on the bottom of the food chain. But he won’t be there for long.</p> <p>After finding a unique core known as Skill-Eater, Edge gains the power to steal the skills of monsters, men, and beasts, and a chance to battle his way up to the top.</p> <p>It seems that his luck has finally changed, although he will soon learn that power never comes without a price.</p> <p><b>Experience an action packed LitRPG adventure set in a world where artifacts known as Cores let their bearers wield the planet’s magic, and where Skills grant superhuman abilities and kaiju roam the wilds. It's perfect for fans of </b><b><i>Solo Leveling</i></b><b>, </b><b><i>The Primal Hunter</i></b><b>, and </b><b><i>1% Lifesteal</i></b><b>!</b></p>"; 
